  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/5f4db29f6e42a7a977056b539d0914cf.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ancient Lovecraftian evil has returned to earth unleashing a deadly flesh organism upon humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One by one the the governments and the infrastructures of humans fell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Aftermath of these events, you are part of what's left of the army and it is up to you to ensure the survival of the human species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/ef221d21627adf898b40e28ee20681b0.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/4ddbd570fa7c22e5cb5dc2e31260c50d.poster.avif?t=1740224544\" width=800 height=449 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/4ddbd570fa7c22e5cb5dc2e31260c50d.webm?t=1740224544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During combat, you take control of your strike team ensuring they will fulfill their objectives and return safely by choosing the optimal equipment and best tactical approach.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >real-time strategy controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"turn-based\" possibility with active pause command mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/7669c8895a8a85a8577e2b885a733db0.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/0b626fe15d35ee92535e471f2bba7819.poster.avif?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/0b626fe15d35ee92535e471f2bba7819.webm?t=1740224544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                          <br>As a commander, you will take control of a military convoy where you can: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >decide the equipment of your strike team </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >assign personnel to different survival tasks </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >craft better equipment </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >research new technologies </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >choose the path you want the convoy to take </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >manage resource priority </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >train your personnel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/914ed5086e3dad11338de070f0a1d145.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 1 - introduction to the game lore and new game options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 2 - The journey begins, assemble your convoy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 3 - Open-World</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 4 - Multiple endings + 2 different totally unique paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, the game folder also contains a Map Editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                     Good luck Commander! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/5f4db29f6e42a7a977056b539d0914cf.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ancient Lovecraftian evil has returned to earth unleashing a deadly flesh organism upon humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One by one the the governments and the infrastructures of humans fell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Aftermath of these events, you are part of what's left of the army and it is up to you to ensure the survival of the human species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/ef221d21627adf898b40e28ee20681b0.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/4ddbd570fa7c22e5cb5dc2e31260c50d.poster.avif?t=1740224544\" width=800 height=449 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/4ddbd570fa7c22e5cb5dc2e31260c50d.webm?t=1740224544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During combat, you take control of your strike team ensuring they will fulfill their objectives and return safely by choosing the optimal equipment and best tactical approach.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >real-time strategy controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"turn-based\" possibility with active pause command mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/7669c8895a8a85a8577e2b885a733db0.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/0b626fe15d35ee92535e471f2bba7819.poster.avif?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/0b626fe15d35ee92535e471f2bba7819.webm?t=1740224544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                          <br>As a commander, you will take control of a military convoy where you can: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >decide the equipment of your strike team </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >assign personnel to different survival tasks </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >craft better equipment </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >research new technologies </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >choose the path you want the convoy to take </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >manage resource priority </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >train your personnel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529770/extras/914ed5086e3dad11338de070f0a1d145.webp?t=1740224544\" width=650 height=35 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 1 - introduction to the game lore and new game options</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 2 - The journey begins, assemble your convoy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 3 - Open-World</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chapter 4 - Multiple endings + 2 different totally unique paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, the game folder also contains a Map Editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                     Good luck Commander! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
